{"type": "article", "id": 2425, "title": "坚果锤", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-18T07:53:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052324206XHxhyYPio3UD5dZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t如今正是吃核桃的季节，如何方便利落地剥核桃的确是件令人困扰的事情。近日，英国设计师 Roger Arquer 设计了一款坚果锤子，简单又实用。Roger Arquer 只是给平常使用地小锤子上增加了一个软硅胶材质的“外套”，使用时只需将核桃塞进去，一锤子敲开便可食用，不会造成满桌或满地飞溅的情况，既方便又干净。这款坚果锤已于本月亮相<a href=\"http://www.maison-objet.com/en\">巴黎 Maison &amp; Objet 贸易展览会</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232419kG7If5TLonWrE3v0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232419lLomev5O9JgRKpMC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}